I'm still letting my
mother down, even now.

516
00:39:47.927 --> 00:39:51.347
Ms. Cha is quite proud of you, though.

517
00:39:52.709 --> 00:39:55.246
It's the result of
a desperate effort, on her part.

518
00:39:55.829 --> 00:39:56.988
Just look.

519
00:39:56.988 --> 00:39:59.044
I usually don't wear
these sorts of clothes.

520
00:39:59.044 --> 00:40:03.615
This is my mom's way of
asserting her dominance over me.

521
00:40:17.880 --> 00:40:22.227
<i>Mooryung Police Station, which is
investigating a missing child case</i>

522
00:40:22.227 --> 00:40:25.822
<i>has arrested Ms. Shin,
the mother of the missing child</i>

523
00:40:25.822 --> 00:40:29.706
<i>this afternoon around 4 p.m.
at a home in Baek Island-dong.</i>

524
00:40:29.706 --> 00:40:32.717
<i>The police, who had been
investigating the missing child</i>

525
00:40:32.717 --> 00:40:34.501
<i>have discovered through CCTV footage</i>

526
00:40:34.501 --> 00:40:40.840
<i>that the mother had
acted violently toward her child.</i>

527
00:40:40.840 --> 00:40:43.452
When people ask me why I like birds

528
00:40:43.452 --> 00:40:45.981
I've never been able to provide them
with a proper answer.

529
00:40:46.534 --> 00:40:50.101
So I've always wanted to meet someone
I didn't need to explain this to...

530
00:40:50.101 --> 00:40:51.959
Please stop right over there.

531
00:40:52.490 --> 00:40:53.595
Over there?

532
00:40:53.595 --> 00:40:54.756
Yes.

533
00:41:13.374 --> 00:41:15.396
Thanks to you, I was able
to get here comfortably.

534
00:41:15.396 --> 00:41:18.095
I did drop you off,
but the ride seemed so short.

535
00:41:19.517 --> 00:41:21.006
Please get home safely.

536
00:41:21.006 --> 00:41:22.124
Um, wait.

537
00:41:23.501 --> 00:41:25.729
Um... goodness.

538
00:41:32.378 --> 00:41:34.642
Um, if you ever have time...

539
00:41:35.675 --> 00:41:37.528
<i>[Parked here for a short while
010-546-7734]</i>

540
00:41:39.193 --> 00:41:40.773
Thank you.

541
00:41:51.093 --> 00:41:55.604
<i>Yes. Ms. Shin, the mother of
Kim Hye Na, who went missing</i>

542
00:41:55.604 --> 00:41:58.943
<i>arrived at Mooryung Police Station
in Gangwon-do not long ago.</i>

543
00:41:58.943 --> 00:42:01.559
<i>In the midst of the missing child's
whereabouts still being unknown</i>

544
00:42:01.559 --> 00:42:05.128
<i>the mother of the missing child
is denying the abuse charges.</i>

545
00:42:08.742 --> 00:42:10.289
<i>I...</i>

546
00:42:11.421 --> 00:42:14.809
<i>took medication several times
while raising Hye Na...</i>

547
00:42:15.688 --> 00:42:18.867
<i>because it was so hard
that I wanted to die!</i>

548
00:42:19.664 --> 00:42:20.883
<i>But...</i>

549
00:42:21.439 --> 00:42:24.284
<i>what do you people know that
