550
00:42:24.284 --> 00:42:27.048
<i>What do you people know?
How dare you treat me this way?</i>

551
00:42:27.775 --> 00:42:31.099
<i>The police, who have taken in the mother
for charges of child abuse</i>

552
00:42:31.099 --> 00:42:34.175
<i>will investigate the child abuse case</i>

553
00:42:34.175 --> 00:42:37.218
<i>and then determine if the child's
disappearance is related to the abuse.</i>

554
00:42:37.218 --> 00:42:41.367
<i>This afternoon, Ms. Shin, the mother
of the missing child from Mooryung</i>

555
00:42:41.367 --> 00:42:43.758
<i>was arrested on account of
child abuse charges...</i>

556
00:42:44.718 --> 00:42:45.918
Yoon Bok.

557
00:42:46.992 --> 00:42:48.486
I'm sorry, Yoon Bok.

558
00:42:48.486 --> 00:42:50.064
Mommy was late.

559
00:42:57.700 --> 00:42:59.246
Are you okay?

560
00:43:00.717 --> 00:43:01.854
Yoon Bok.

561
00:43:01.854 --> 00:43:03.233
Yoon Bok!

562
00:43:04.972 --> 00:43:06.394
I'm sorry.

563
00:43:06.994 --> 00:43:09.454
Mommy should have
gotten back here sooner.

564
00:43:09.454 --> 00:43:10.831
But I was late.

565
00:43:10.831 --> 00:43:12.530
I'm sorry, Yoon Bok.

566
00:43:16.742 --> 00:43:18.845
Was Mom...

567
00:43:19.311 --> 00:43:21.756
Was Hye Na's mom...

568
00:43:22.461 --> 00:43:25.005
really angry?

569
00:43:28.211 --> 00:43:30.331
That person isn't your mom.

570
00:43:30.988 --> 00:43:32.758
And you're not Hye Na, either.

571
00:43:33.200 --> 00:43:34.807
You're Yoon Bok.

572
00:43:34.807 --> 00:43:36.805
And Yoon Bok's mom is me.

573
00:43:37.586 --> 00:43:40.468
But, what if people...

574
00:43:41.697 --> 00:43:45.764
take away Yoon Bok's mom, too?

575
00:43:52.575 --> 00:43:58.159
<i>There have been no leads in identifying
the location of the missing child.</i>

576
00:43:58.159 --> 00:44:01.630
<i>And amidst all this, it has been revealed
that Ms. Shin, her mother, abused her.</i>

577
00:44:01.630 --> 00:44:05.291
<i>So many people are
wondering if her mother</i>

578
00:44:05.291 --> 00:44:09.119
<i>had something to do
with the child's disappearance.</i>

579
00:44:09.119 --> 00:44:12.611
<i>The police found an alibi for the
mother during the investigation</i>

580
00:44:12.611 --> 00:44:15.394
<i>so it'll be difficult to
prove that her abuse was</i>

581
00:44:15.394 --> 00:44:18.101
<i>linked to the child's
disappearance, won't it?</i>

582
00:44:18.101 --> 00:44:20.999
<i>Yes, but if this had been
planned beforehand</i>

583
00:44:20.999 --> 00:44:22.898
<i>the situation will
become more complicated.</i>

584
00:44:33.303 --> 00:44:34.901
Damn it.

585
00:44:51.146 --> 00:44:52.941
Yoon Bok, are you okay...

586
00:44:53.325 --> 00:44:54.332
Oh my gosh.

587
00:44:54.332 --> 00:44:55.570
You're burning up!

588
00:45:02.365 --> 00:45:03.660
Look at how much you're sweating!

589
00:45:03.660 --> 00:45:04.760
Yoon Bok.

590
00:45:04.760 --> 00:45:06.881
Can you hear me? Huh?

591
00:45:06.881 --> 00:45:08.639
Answer me if you can hear me.

592
00:45:08.639 --> 00:45:10.486
Okay? Yoon Bok.

593
00:45:17.930 --> 00:45:19.793
I'm calling from Suite 816.

594
00:45:19.793 --> 00:45:22.653
Do you have any fever-relieving medicine?

595
00:45:23.177 --> 00:45:25.637
No, it's fine.
We don't need to go to the hospital.

596
00:45:29.323 --> 00:45:30.463
Oh gosh, what do I do now?

597
00:45:30.463 --> 00:45:31.907
Get it together.
Get it together.

598
00:45:55.227 --> 00:45:57.251
Hello, this is Kang Soo Jin.

599
00:46:02.847 --> 00:46:03.877
Um...

600
00:46:08.680 --> 00:46:10.425
Seven years old?
Eight years old?

601
00:46:10.425 --> 00:46:12.359
She just turned nine.

602
00:46:12.359 --> 00:46:13.847
- Her clothes, please.
- Sure.

603
00:46:19.660 --> 00:46:20.696
What's her name?

604
00:46:21.207 --> 00:46:23.216
It's Yoon Bok.
Kim Yoon Bok.

605
00:46:23.216 --> 00:46:24.350
Yoon Bok.

606
00:46:26.595 --> 00:46:28.459
- Can you sit her up?
- Yes.

607
00:46:39.412 --> 00:46:40.528
All done.

608
00:46:47.220 --> 00:46:48.372
Yoon Bok.

609
00:46:48.372 --> 00:46:50.600
Say "Ah," Yoon Bok.

610
00:46:52.330 --> 00:46:54.856
Open wide. Good job.

611
00:47:00.428 --> 00:47:01.843
It's inflamed.

612
00:47:01.843 --> 00:47:03.388
She has laryngitis.

613
00:47:04.162 --> 00:47:05.720
Since when has she been unwell?

614
00:47:06.292 --> 00:47:08.495
She's been coughing
since yesterday afternoon

615
00:47:08.495 --> 00:47:10.655
and she vomited once before bed.

616
00:47:12.421 --> 00:47:15.126
Her larynx is badly swollen.

617
00:47:15.126 --> 00:47:17.934
If it gets any more swollen,
she may have to go to the ER.

618
00:47:18.964 --> 00:47:20.995
You must take her to
the hospital tomorrow.

619
00:47:22.039 --> 00:47:23.225
Do you understand?

620
00:47:30.472 --> 00:47:32.530
Please fill the tub with hot water.

621
00:47:44.751 --> 00:47:46.754
Is she conscious?

622
00:47:47.289 --> 00:47:49.051
It's because she has a high fever.

623
00:47:49.051 --> 00:47:52.711
Her fever would go down and her coughs
would become less severe after 30 minutes

624
00:47:52.711 --> 00:47:55.089
but, um, the air in the room is too dry.

625
00:47:55.562 --> 00:47:57.999
Go to the front desk
and ask for a humidifier.

626
00:47:57.999 --> 00:47:59.151
All right.

627
00:48:00.984 --> 00:48:02.986
All right, there we go.

628
00:48:10.059 --> 00:48:11.296
Mom.

629
00:48:15.044 --> 00:48:16.327
Yoon Bok.

630
00:48:17.042 --> 00:48:18.397
Are you conscious now?

631
00:48:23.039 --> 00:48:25.044
Can you say your name?

632
00:48:26.182 --> 00:48:27.843
What is your name?

633
00:48:31.519 --> 00:48:33.120
Kim Hye Na.

634
00:48:35.868 --> 00:48:37.870
Can you... repeat your
name for me...

635
00:48:37.870 --> 00:48:38.897
Yoon Bok?

636
00:48:40.571 --> 00:48:42.006
Kim Hye Na.

637
00:48:47.419 --> 00:48:49.048
What about your mom's name?

638
00:48:49.941 --> 00:48:51.934
Shin Ja Young.

639
00:49:04.573 --> 00:49:07.120
This could turn into
acute bronchitis or pneumonia

640
00:49:07.120 --> 00:49:08.711
so you must take her
to the hospital.

641
00:49:12.591 --> 00:49:15.312
Is there... a reason why you
can't take her to the hospital?

642
00:49:19.613 --> 00:49:21.584
Come to my hospital and
pick up medicine for her.

643
00:49:21.584 --> 00:49:24.584
And make sure to give her all of it.
I'll give you a call after three days.

644
00:49:26.267 --> 00:49:27.827
Thank you.

645
00:49:28.582 --> 00:49:30.801
This place isn't good for a young child.

646
00:49:31.450 --> 00:49:33.254
Can't you go to your mother's place?

647
00:49:37.705 --> 00:49:38.707
Oh.

648
00:49:38.707 --> 00:49:40.919
There are three rooms at my place.

649
00:49:40.919 --> 00:49:42.428
But I live alone.

650
00:49:42.899 --> 00:49:45.600
I leave early in the morning
and come home late at night.

651
00:49:46.464 --> 00:49:48.026
If you need me,
please give me a call.

652
00:49:49.926 --> 00:49:51.548
Um, Doctor.

653
00:49:58.055 --> 00:49:59.307
You're thankful, right?

654
00:50:02.144 --> 00:50:03.493
All right.

655
00:50:03.493 --> 00:50:05.120
Let's talk later.

656
00:50:34.986 --> 00:50:37.019
She's been sleeping for 20 hours now.

657
00:50:37.019 --> 00:50:39.397
I think she took a ton
of sleeping pills.

658
00:50:39.397 --> 00:50:42.459
We can't investigate her
if she's not fully conscious.

659
00:50:48.381 --> 00:50:50.559
<i>What about the man she lives with?
Did you locate him?</i>

660
00:50:50.559 --> 00:50:53.865
<i>He hasn't picked up his phone
since that day.</i>

661
00:51:16.993 --> 00:51:21.019
<i>[Samhwa Barber Shop]</i>

662
00:51:25.707 --> 00:51:26.984
Thank you.

663
00:51:39.164 --> 00:51:41.017
Is she... sick?

664
00:51:41.495 --> 00:51:44.908
I'm sorry, but please take care
of Yoon Bok for a bit.

665
00:52:15.528 --> 00:52:17.457
I finally know what that sound is.

666
00:52:17.939 --> 00:52:21.626
Jingle... jangle... jingle.

667
00:52:29.914 --> 00:52:30.977
This?

668
00:52:31.408 --> 00:52:34.513
I bet you always get caught
when you play hide-and-seek

669
00:52:34.513 --> 00:52:35.747
because of that sound.

670
00:52:45.030 --> 00:52:47.604
- Hello.
- Hello.

671
00:52:47.604 --> 00:52:48.908
You're here, Big Sis?

672
00:52:49.341 --> 00:52:50.519
Where's Mom?

673
00:52:50.986 --> 00:52:52.111
She's resting.

674
00:52:55.827 --> 00:52:58.053
She's resting since she's sick!

675
00:52:59.379 --> 00:53:00.743
Mom.

676
00:53:00.743 --> 00:53:01.756
Oh!

677
00:53:01.756 --> 00:53:03.004
You're here?

678
00:53:05.354 --> 00:53:06.990
This won't work.

679
00:53:07.568 --> 00:53:09.169
I definitely will
repay you your money.

680
00:53:09.169 --> 00:53:11.611
But I can't let you
treat me as you please...

681
00:53:12.091 --> 00:53:13.461
just because you lent me money.

682
00:53:13.461 --> 00:53:15.513
What are you talking about, Soo Jin?

683
00:53:15.513 --> 00:53:18.059
Say it clearly,
in a way that I'll understand.

684
00:53:19.573 --> 00:53:21.879
Wearing the clothes you like.

685
00:53:21.879 --> 00:53:24.687
Going on a date with
a man that you like.

686
00:53:24.687 --> 00:53:26.738
I did so much of that in the past.

687
00:53:28.361 --> 00:53:31.298
I said that I'd meet with you
to spend time with you

688
00:53:31.298 --> 00:53:34.227
not that I'd readjust my life
to suit you again.

689
00:53:34.934 --> 00:53:36.028
Big Sis.

690
00:53:40.019 --> 00:53:42.131
You're so selfish, Big Sis.

691
00:53:42.597 --> 00:53:44.102
You left without a word.

692
00:53:44.102 --> 00:53:46.140
Do you know how upset Mom was

693
00:53:46.140 --> 00:53:48.077
and how much she must
have missed you, that...

694
00:53:48.077 --> 00:53:49.872
even though she has cancer...

695
00:53:52.952 --> 00:53:55.472
someone like her,
who is so scared of hospitals

696
00:53:55.472 --> 00:53:57.959
got chemo and underwent
surgery by herself?

697
00:53:57.959 --> 00:54:01.388
And this time, her cancer relapsed,
and it's been so hard for all of us!

698
00:54:01.388 --> 00:54:02.955
And yet, you...

699
00:54:02.955 --> 00:54:05.077
went off and did
everything you wanted to...

700
00:54:05.077 --> 00:54:06.890
Go outside, Yi Jin.

701
00:54:06.890 --> 00:54:09.604
What did Mom do that was
so wrong, Big Sis?

702
00:54:09.604 --> 00:54:11.754
She's done so much for you!

703
00:54:11.754 --> 00:54:13.700
Yi Jin, go outside. Please.

704
00:54:22.368 --> 00:54:23.577
Mom.

705
00:54:24.794 --> 00:54:26.544
You have cancer?

706
00:54:35.600 --> 00:54:37.365
Why didn't you tell me?

707
00:54:40.660 --> 00:54:43.354
I didn't get cancer because of you.

708
00:54:44.323 --> 00:54:46.629
Remember how my mom passed
away because of breast cancer

709
00:54:46.629 --> 00:54:48.537
when I was a second year in high school?

710
00:54:51.513 --> 00:54:53.888
I was so angry then.

711
00:54:54.390 --> 00:54:56.537
I felt as if she'd
left me behind on purpose.

712
00:54:57.568 --> 00:55:00.350
And after that,
I was determined to never get cancer.

713
00:55:00.995 --> 00:55:02.457
In case you girls would get mad.

714
00:55:07.537 --> 00:55:08.955
Soo Jin.

715
00:55:10.655 --> 00:55:12.370
I knew you'd come back.

716
00:55:13.760 --> 00:55:18.193
That's why I bravely underwent chemo and
got surgery by myself, seven years ago.

717
00:55:18.193 --> 00:55:20.519
So that I could be healthy
when I welcomed you back.

718
00:55:21.671 --> 00:55:24.321
But then, I heard that
it had relapsed, and...

719
00:55:25.823 --> 00:55:27.484
I got a bit scared.

720
00:55:32.042 --> 00:55:34.903
I had no idea
where in the world you were

721
00:55:34.903 --> 00:55:38.010
and whether you were even alive or dead.

722
00:55:39.214 --> 00:55:42.147
And I was scared that
I'd die here, all alone.

723
00:55:44.522 --> 00:55:45.711
Mom.

724
00:55:48.990 --> 00:55:50.687
Will you stay with me?

725
00:55:59.466 --> 00:56:01.048
Mom, I...

726
00:56:01.048 --> 00:56:02.173
Must you go?

727
00:56:12.124 --> 00:56:14.874
Can't you at least meet with me
10 times before you leave again?

728
00:56:25.321 --> 00:56:27.024
Also, you...

729
00:56:27.484 --> 00:56:30.062
don't usually care
about the clothes you wear.

730
00:56:30.591 --> 00:56:33.269
So what's so wrong about you
wearing the clothes I buy for you?

731
00:56:33.269 --> 00:56:35.506
Also, about Doctor Jung.

732
00:56:36.120 --> 00:56:38.716
He definitely isn't the
type of guy that I like.

733
00:56:39.609 --> 00:56:41.859
He's the type of guy who spends
seven days a week at the hospital

734
00:56:41.859 --> 00:56:43.821
and eats all three of his meals
per day at the hospital.

735
00:56:43.821 --> 00:56:46.046
Are you afraid that I'll try to
set you up with him?

736
00:56:49.765 --> 00:56:52.658
I'm going to pretend that
I didn't hear what you said before

737
00:56:52.658 --> 00:56:54.839
about repaying the money and such.

738
00:56:55.526 --> 00:56:57.468
I'm tired, so get going now.

739
00:56:57.468 --> 00:57:00.370
And don't count today among the 10
days I have. That wouldn't be fair.

740
00:57:06.562 --> 00:57:08.571
<i>[Mooryung Police Station]</i>

741
00:57:08.571 --> 00:57:09.816
<i>But...</i>

742
00:57:11.022 --> 00:57:12.053
no matter how much I think about it

743
00:57:12.053 --> 00:57:14.466
I don't think the child
went there to die.

744
00:57:14.466 --> 00:57:17.044
Look at her pace and her movements.

745
00:57:17.044 --> 00:57:19.781
Don't you think that she'd be smiling
if we could see her face?

746
00:57:20.481 --> 00:57:22.537
You're letting your emotions
cloud your judgment.

747
00:57:22.537 --> 00:57:26.651
Nobody wants to see a child
walking toward her death, after all.

748
00:57:27.437 --> 00:57:32.283
To me, it looks like Hye Na
is saying her final farewell.

749
00:57:32.283 --> 00:57:35.339
Like she's saying,
"Bye, you guys. Take care."

750
00:57:35.339 --> 00:57:36.430
Like this.

751
00:57:36.430 --> 00:57:38.126
9 times out of 10, in cases like this

752
00:57:38.126 --> 00:57:41.720
the case is closed with the body
of the child being discovered.

753
00:57:42.220 --> 00:57:45.055
But I just can't give up on the
possibility of that 10 percent chance.

754
00:57:45.055 --> 00:57:46.624
For example.

755
00:57:46.624 --> 00:57:51.769
The lady living next door or a teacher
from her school could've taken her away.

756
00:57:51.769 --> 00:57:52.850
Maybe...

757
00:57:52.850 --> 00:57:56.115
someone like that teacher
who is a bird researcher.

758
00:57:56.115 --> 00:57:57.984
You mean the temporary homeroom teacher?

759
00:57:57.984 --> 00:58:00.214
She's definitely not the type
to do such a thing!

760
00:58:00.214 --> 00:58:02.872
She has no interest in
other people's problems.

761
00:58:02.872 --> 00:58:04.539
And she hates kids, too.

762
00:58:06.691 --> 00:58:07.885
Really?

763
00:58:07.885 --> 00:58:09.821
I didn't take you to be
this kind of person

764
00:58:09.821 --> 00:58:12.332
but you kind of have
a naive side to you, Detective.

765
00:58:34.600 --> 00:58:36.307
I'm back.

766
00:58:37.131 --> 00:58:38.691
Where's Yoon Bok?

767
00:58:47.198 --> 00:58:50.405
Third floor.
It's the rooftop suite.

768
01:00:33.620 --> 01:00:34.638
All right.

769
01:00:34.638 --> 01:00:37.812
Shall we go and
play hide-and-seek?

770
01:00:53.825 --> 01:00:57.944
<i>[Call Me Mother / Mother]</i>

771
01:00:59.789 --> 01:01:06.789
Subtitles by DramaFever

772
01:01:12.466 --> 01:01:15.374
<i>I can't have anyone
take my Soo Jin away.</i>

773
01:01:15.374 --> 01:01:18.633
<i>I won't go anywhere,
and wait right here.</i>

774
01:01:18.633 --> 01:01:22.109
<i>It's in a mother's nature to not be able
to die and leave her child by herself.</i>

775
01:01:22.109 --> 01:01:24.138
<i>You're not being
held by me anymore.</i>

776
01:01:24.138 --> 01:01:26.475
<i>Go anywhere you want.
Fly away and be free.</i>

777
01:01:26.475 --> 01:01:29.964
<i>Every time you call my name, Mom,
I think to myself that I'm your child.</i>

778
01:01:29.964 --> 01:01:31.466
<i>Why did Won Hee die?</i>

779
01:01:31.466 --> 01:01:33.158
<i>You have to tell me the real reason.</i>

780
01:01:33.158 --> 01:01:35.885
<i>Do you know Ms. Kang Soo Jin?
Look into who she really is.</i>

781
01:01:35.885 --> 01:01:37.977
<i>I'm going to keep this.</i>

782
01:01:37.977 --> 01:01:40.149
<i>What is this, Yoon Bok?</i>

783
01:01:40.149 --> 01:01:42.042
<i>Where did you get this?</i>

